<% if @charge.present? %>
<div class="grid-x"  style="padding: 40px 0; background-color: #404041;">
	<div class="cell small-12 medium-8 medium-offset-2 text-center">
		<table>
			<tr>
				<td width="50%"><h4 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Disclosure Statement PDF</h4></td>
				<td><a href="https://res.cloudinary.com/thypowerhouse/image/upload/v1538601209/Disclosure_Statement.pdf" class="button primary success large expanded" style="border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #b2b71f; color: #fff;" target="_blank">DOWNLOAD NOW</a></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="text-left" style="line-height: 20px; ">
					<div style="padding: 20px">Is a legal document that is used to gather further and better particulars in regards to an alleged debt procured, assigned or purchased by debt collectors. The Disclosure Statement can be sent to debt collectors in response to their claims of an alleged debt despite them providing a Notice of Assignment.</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

		<table>
			<tr>
				<td width="50%"><h4 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">No Contract=No Consent=No Law PDF</h4></td>
				<td><a href="https://res.cloudinary.com/thypowerhouse/image/upload/v1538601207/No_Contract_Consent_Law.pdf" class="button primary success large expanded" style="border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #b2b71f; color: #fff;" target="_blank">DOWNLOAD NOW</a></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="text-left" style="line-height: 20px; ">
					<div style="padding: 20px">Is a legal document to notify debt collectors that you intend to file a notice to produce certified copies of an alleged debt. The No Contract=No Consent=No Law PDF is to be used in the event debt collectors continue to refuse or acknowledge your legal right to further and better particulars. All parties have a legal right to obtain further and better particulars in regards to an alleged debt and in some cases a subpoena may be needed. If in the event you have received a notice of assignment without further and better particulars this PDF can be used to seek the actual Deed of Novation (Proof of Debt).</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

		<table>
			<tr>
				<td width="50%"><h4 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Harassment by Interloper PDF</h4></td>
				<td><a href="https://res.cloudinary.com/thypowerhouse/image/upload/v1538601209/Harrasment_by_Interloper.pdf" class="button primary success large expanded" style="border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #b2b71f; color: #fff;" target="_blank">DOWNLOAD NOW</a></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="text-left" style="line-height: 20px; ">
					<div style="padding: 20px">Is a legal cease and desist notice sent to debt collectors/interlopers to stop all contact by telephone. Upon sending this document you must provide an address, postal or email for debt collectors to continue correspond. (Written only). The Harassment by Interloper PDF may be used at anytime you feel threatened, bullied or intimidated, if in the event debt collectors ignore this notice and continue to harass then you have the right to report to police and demand your rights be protected.</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>


	</div>
</div>
<% end %>